</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><span style="color:#6BAB30;"><a href="/scp-1615">PROGRAMME BENTIU-5 - CANCELLED DUE TO SECURITY CONCERNS.</a></span></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Comment: <em>I know it is a shame, but let this be a fairly benign warning for all of us. Had that crop reached the open market, the backlash on the food industry could have been huge, and I am not talking about the owners, I mean the workers that would be laid down world-wide. The bigger picture, people! We want to change the world, yes, but not if we destroy entire economies faster that we, or anyone, can rebuild them. And, for that matter, who warned the</em> other <em>Foundation?</em> What is Mission Watch <em>DOING?</em> - Director Maxwell, Logistics.</li>
</ul>
